import React from "react";
import {
  Box,
  Heading,
  Link,
  Image,
  Text,
  Divider,
  HStack,
  Tag,
  Wrap,
  WrapItem,
  SpaceProps,
  useColorModeValue,
  Container,
  VStack,
  Grid,
  GridItem
} from "@chakra-ui/react";
const Recipes = () => {
  return <Container maxW={"7xl"} p="12">
  <Heading as="h1" fontSize='50px'>Health Japanese Fried Rice</Heading>
  <Grid templateColumns='repeat(5, 1fr)' gap={4} marginTop="40px">
  <GridItem w='70%' h='10'></GridItem>
  <GridItem w='100%' h='10' bg='blue.500' ></GridItem>
  <GridItem w='100%' h='10' bg='blue.500' ></GridItem>
  <GridItem w='100%' h='10' bg='blue.500' ></GridItem>
</Grid>

  </Container>;
};

export default Recipes;
